    "Annotators labeled positive mentions of a variable as present.",
    "Negation or absent mentions were both treated similarly.",
    "Ambiguous instances were marked as uncertain.",
    "12 notes in the Stanford MOUD Dataset and 8 notes in CheXpert had conflicting duplicate-annotated labels for IRR.",
    "These notes were excluded from the held-out test sets."
